## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for family.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers family visibility,
membership-aware display,
care/responsibility-aware surfaces,
historical family reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- family identity must resolve
- membership basis must resolve
- care/responsibility scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid family identity
- invalid membership basis
- invalid responsibility scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish family state,
membership state,
responsibility scope,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- family runtime scope is explicit
- membership-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
